(931, 'onlinecourseportal', 'Through research-based programs and innovative techniques, Mather LifeWays Institute on Aging is committed to advancing the field of eldercare. Used by individuals and entire organizations, our nationally recognized, award-winning programs include training modules, online\n				courses, toolkits, and learning modules designed to make learning fun and easy.'),
