(1319, 'onlinecourseportal', 'Profile & Surveys'),
(1320, 'onlinecourseportal', 'Profile &amp; Surveys'),
(1321, 'onlinecourseportal', 'Surveys'),
(1322, 'onlinecourseportal', 'Our surveys are designed to help us obtain information that help with decision-making. Our goal is to help better educate our participants by creating a client touch-point, a feedback system, and means to better understanding the shifting needs of the field.'),
(1323, 'surveyor', 'Extended Profile Survey'),
(1324, 'surveyor', '<p>Please complete the following survey to help us learn more about our users. Your responses will be kept confidential.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />'),
(1325, 'surveyor', '1. What is your age?'),
(1326, 'surveyor', '2. How would you describe your current role as a family caregiver?'),
(1327, 'surveyor', '3. If you are currently a caregiver for an older parent, relative, or friend, about how many hours a week do you spend caregiving or providing some type of help to this person?'),
(1328, 'surveyor', '4. Which of the following problems have you experienced as a caregiver?  If you are not currently caregiving, which of the following problems do you anticipate in your future role as a caregiver? (check all that apply)'),
(1329, 'surveyor', '5. If you are currently a caregiver for an older parent, relative, or friend, about how many full or partial scheduled workdays did you miss during the past 6 months due to your caregiving responsibilities?'),
(1330, 'surveyor', 'Online Workforce Support<br />Pre-Course Survey'),
(1331, 'surveyor', '<p>Please complete the following survey to help us learn more about how this course benefits participants in becoming more effective caregivers for older parents or other relatives or friends.  Some of the questions are designed to learn about how caregiving impacts your work and home life.  You will be asked to complete another survey at the end of this course.  Each survey takes less than 5 minutes to complete.  Your responses will be kept confidential.</p>\r\n<p> - 22 Questions</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />'),
(1332, 'surveyor', '<i>Here are some thoughts and feelings that people sometimes have about themselves as caregivers. How much does each statement describe your thoughts about your caregiving?</i>'),
(1333, 'surveyor', '1. How much do you believe that you know how to deal with difficult caregiving situations?'),
(1334, 'surveyor', '2. How much do you feel that, all in all, you’re a good caregiver?'),
(1335, 'surveyor', '<i>Sometimes people can learn things about themselves from taking care of a close relative or friend.</i>'),
(1336, 'surveyor', '3. As a result of caregiving, how much have you become more aware of your inner strengths?'),
(1337, 'surveyor', '4. As a result of caregiving, how much have you become more self-confident?'),
(1338, 'surveyor', 'Caregivers sometimes feel that they lose important things in life because of caring for a close relative or friend.  To what extent do you feel that you personally have lost the following?'),
(1339, 'surveyor', '5. How much have you lost a sense of who you are?'),
(1340, 'surveyor', '6. How much have you lost an important part of yourself?'),
(1341, 'surveyor', 'For working caregivers, caregiving may impact one’s performance and productivity in the work environment.  These next questions address some areas of your work that may be impacted by caregiving responsibilities.'),
(1342, 'surveyor', '7. Because of my caregiving responsibilities, I feel that I am not always able to focus my full attention on my work.'),
(1343, 'surveyor', '8. Because of caregiving responsibilities, how often do you need to take time off, come in the office later, or leave the office earlier?'),
(1344, 'surveyor', '9. Because of caregiving responsibilities, the stress of meeting my work demands keep me from doing my best.'),
(1345, 'surveyor', '10. During the past 12 months, have you considered any of the following because of your caregiving responsibilities?'),
(1346, 'surveyor', '<i>Caregiving may also impact one’s personal life and health. These next questions address some areas of your personal life that may be impacted by caregiving responsibilities.</i>'),
(1347, 'surveyor', '11. I spend so much time caregiving that I do not take time for myself.'),
(1348, 'surveyor', '12. The stress of balancing work, personal, and caregiving responsibilities affects my health.'),
(1349, 'surveyor', '13. I have enough energy to accomplish the tasks that are important to me.'),
